entries.arrival_phase_1: pcontrast3 Beissa : < pcontrast1 You appear to have gotten their attention, your next target is coming to you now. pcontrast3 >
entries.arrival_phase_2: pcontrast3 Beissa: < pcontrast1 There they are, track them down before they can locate you. pcontrast3  >
entries.assassinate_success: pcontrast3 Beissa: < pcontrast3 I think I heard Our Lady screaming all the way from Mos Eisley. She has a wonderful voice. pcontrast3 >
entries.destroy_escort: pcontrast3 Beissa: < pcontrast1 Leave none alive.  Do not think that for a moment they might have spared you. pcontrast3 >
entries.escort_remaining: pcontrast3 Tactical Computer: < pcontrast1 An escorting craft has been destroyed, %DI remain. pcontrast3 >
entries.escort_wiped_out: pcontrast3 Tactical Computer: < pcontrast1 All escorting craft have been destroyed. pcontrast3 >
entries.failed_escape: pcontrast3 Beissa: < pcontrast1 Valarian's new hired killer managed to elude you.  Perhaps she was right in letting you get away. pcontrast3 >
entries.quest_location_d: An area of space around the gas giant Yavin
entries.quest_target_d: A defected Imperial pilot living a mercenary life to avoid the Empire
entries.split_quest_alert: pcontrast3 Beissa: < pcontrast1 Your third target will be in Yavin shortly.  This is all going very well, you might just work out yet. pcontrast3 >
entries.title: Yavin System: Hunt down Valarian replacements (continued)
entries.title_d: Continue destroying the Valarian Replacements, part 2 of 3.
